  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, randomized study comparing VATS( Video-Assisted Thoracoscopy ) to
      reinsertion of a Thoracostomy Tube in patients with retained haemothorax. The hypothesis is
      that early VATS as opposed to reinsertion of a thoracostomy tube , will lead to less
      complications and shorter hospital stay.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
